    "The generator is responsible for producing fresh examples, while the discriminator assesses the disparities between the generated content and the pre-existing content [38].",
    "These disparities are subsequently relayed to the generator ANN, influencing its content generation process.",
    "This iterative mechanism continually enhances the performance of the GAI system with each cycle, progressing until the generated content becomes indistinguishable from the existing content.",
    "Notably, both ANNs undergo concurrent training and become increasingly proficient as the generator refines its content production, while the discriminator hones its detection abilities.",
    "Although GANs exhibit the capability to yield high-quality samples swiftly, their sample diversity is relatively limited."
